snippet.title: Firestorm Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
"Its time you saw the future while you still have human eyes!" 
- Kane

Welcome to Firestorm; the first person shooter that Tiberian Sun deserves. Explore brand new game modes, infantry, vehicles, structures and maps in the Tiberian Sun Era.

Can't wait for Firestorm? Head on over to https://totemarts.games/ and jump in game! You might find a few crates with some... "special" vehicles.

Like and subscribe if you like what you see!

Join us on Discord! We hold PUGs (Pick Up Games) every weekend at 6:00pm GMT or 2:00pm EDT
https://discord.gg/totemarts
